data.description: *Motivated seller- bring offers!* No need to wait on building! Gorgeous Home that is practically NEW! Entry Foyer brings you past the Large Dining Room for Easy Entertaining. Open Floor Plan with a Beautiful Kitchen overlooking the Great Room and Breakfast area. Quartz Countertop, Stainless Steel appliances, Upgraded Stove/Oven, and a Farmer's sink. Walk in Pantry and a Breakfast Bar completes this Gourmet Kitchen. Office on Main Level could easily be converted into a Bedroom. Mud area right off the garage is convenient. Fully Fenced backyard provide extra privacy. Spacious Loft at the top of the stairs. Huge Primary Bedroom with tray ceiling. The Primary Bathroom is luxurious with a separate Garden Tub, Raised Vanity and a glass enclosed shower with bench seating. Quartz Countertop and higher sinks in all bathrooms. Most of the rooms are prewired for a ceiling fan. One of the largest floor plans in the neighborhood! No rental restrictions
